[
  {
    "bundleId": "b0",
    "bundleIndex": 0,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-0.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-0.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Lisa did not think her life could break down so fast and so completely.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5.026,
        "duration": 5.026,
        "sentenceIndex": 0
      },
      {
        "text": "One moment, she had a home, a job, and a family, but then everything changed.",
        "startTime": 5.026,
        "endTime": 11.076,
        "duration": 6.05,
        "sentenceIndex": 1
      },
      {
        "text": "In the next moment, she had no things left because everything was gone.",
        "startTime": 11.076,
        "endTime": 16.252,
        "duration": 5.176,
        "sentenceIndex": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "The story began with a phone call that changed everything for Lisa and James.",
        "startTime": 16.252,
        "endTime": 21.702,
        "duration": 5.45,
        "sentenceIndex": 3
      },
      {
        "text": "Her husband was in an accident, so she was very worried.",
        "startTime": 21.702,
        "endTime": 25.816,
        "duration": 4.114,
        "sentenceIndex": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "When Lisa arrived at the hospital, he was already gone.",
        "startTime": 25.816,
        "endTime": 29.859,
        "duration": 4.043,
        "sentenceIndex": 5
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 29.859025,
    "measuredDuration": 29.859025
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b1",
    "bundleIndex": 1,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-1.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-1.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Lisa was seven months pregnant, but then she became a widow with two kids.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5.036,
        "duration": 5.036,
        "sentenceIndex": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "The weeks after were full of sadness and fear for Lisa and her friends.",
        "startTime": 5.036,
        "endTime": 9.723,
        "duration": 4.687,
        "sentenceIndex": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa did not have any money saved for the future.",
        "startTime": 9.723,
        "endTime": 12.958,
        "duration": 3.235,
        "sentenceIndex": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "She lost her job just before the accident happened.",
        "startTime": 12.958,
        "endTime": 16.325,
        "duration": 3.367,
        "sentenceIndex": 9
      },
      {
        "text": "She had no family nearby, so she could not get help.",
        "startTime": 16.325,
        "endTime": 19.908,
        "duration": 3.583,
        "sentenceIndex": 10
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa moved into a small apartment with her children, James, Emily, and baby Noah.",
        "startTime": 19.908,
        "endTime": 25.706,
        "duration": 5.798,
        "sentenceIndex": 11
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 25.70576,
    "measuredDuration": 25.70576
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b2",
    "bundleIndex": 2,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-2.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-2.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Lisa wanted to find work, but who would hire a mother with three kids.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5.174,
        "duration": 5.174,
        "sentenceIndex": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "She took any jobs she could find, like cleaning houses and working in fast food.",
        "startTime": 5.174,
        "endTime": 11.067,
        "duration": 5.892,
        "sentenceIndex": 13
      },
      {
        "text": "The work was very tiring, so I needed a break afterward.",
        "startTime": 11.067,
        "endTime": 15.236,
        "duration": 4.17,
        "sentenceIndex": 14
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa comes home late and feels tired, but she still cooks dinner and helps the kids.",
        "startTime": 15.236,
        "endTime": 21.416,
        "duration": 6.179,
        "sentenceIndex": 15
      },
      {
        "text": "Some nights, Lisa sits in her car after work and cries quietly.",
        "startTime": 21.416,
        "endTime": 26.088,
        "duration": 4.672,
        "sentenceIndex": 16
      },
      {
        "text": "She felt like no one could see her, so she was very sad.",
        "startTime": 26.088,
        "endTime": 30.257,
        "duration": 4.17,
        "sentenceIndex": 17
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 30.257392,
    "measuredDuration": 30.257392
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b3",
    "bundleIndex": 3,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-3.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-3.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "The people whose houses Lisa cleaned did not know her name at all.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.672,
        "duration": 4.672,
        "sentenceIndex": 18
      },
      {
        "text": "They saw her as a cleaner, not as a real person with feelings.",
        "startTime": 4.672,
        "endTime": 9.212,
        "duration": 4.539,
        "sentenceIndex": 19
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa cleaned toilets and vacuumed carpets, then went home to her small apartment with children.",
        "startTime": 9.212,
        "endTime": 16.087,
        "duration": 6.875,
        "sentenceIndex": 20
      },
      {
        "text": "The stress felt very strong and made everything seem hard for Lisa and James.",
        "startTime": 16.087,
        "endTime": 21.538,
        "duration": 5.451,
        "sentenceIndex": 21
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa felt very sad, like she was sinking in deep water.",
        "startTime": 21.538,
        "endTime": 25.582,
        "duration": 4.044,
        "sentenceIndex": 22
      },
      {
        "text": "She could not sleep because she was worried about her friend Lisa.",
        "startTime": 25.582,
        "endTime": 30.254,
        "duration": 4.672,
        "sentenceIndex": 23
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 30.254399,
    "measuredDuration": 30.254399
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b4",
    "bundleIndex": 4,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-4.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-4.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She could not eat because she felt very sick that day.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.749,
        "duration": 3.749,
        "sentenceIndex": 24
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa woke up at night, worried about money and how to care for her children.",
        "startTime": 3.749,
        "endTime": 9.174,
        "duration": 5.426,
        "sentenceIndex": 25
      },
      {
        "text": "Some nights, dark thoughts come into Lisa's mind and make her feel sad.",
        "startTime": 9.174,
        "endTime": 14.253,
        "duration": 5.079,
        "sentenceIndex": 26
      },
      {
        "text": "What will happen if she decides to give up now.",
        "startTime": 14.253,
        "endTime": 17.516,
        "duration": 3.263,
        "sentenceIndex": 27
      },
      {
        "text": "What would happen if she stopped trying to succeed.",
        "startTime": 17.516,
        "endTime": 21.056,
        "duration": 3.54,
        "sentenceIndex": 28
      },
      {
        "text": "The thoughts scared her because they were always there and felt very heavy.",
        "startTime": 21.056,
        "endTime": 26.262,
        "duration": 5.206,
        "sentenceIndex": 29
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 26.262404,
    "measuredDuration": 26.262404
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b5",
    "bundleIndex": 5,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-5.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-5.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "One Friday night, Lisa knelt on her small apartment floor after a hard week.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5.972,
        "duration": 5.972,
        "sentenceIndex": 30
      },
      {
        "text": "The children were asleep in their beds, so it was very quiet.",
        "startTime": 5.972,
        "endTime": 10.795,
        "duration": 4.823,
        "sentenceIndex": 31
      },
      {
        "text": "The apartment was very quiet, so Lisa and James could relax there.",
        "startTime": 10.795,
        "endTime": 16.001,
        "duration": 5.206,
        "sentenceIndex": 32
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa felt very alone and broken inside, so she needed help.",
        "startTime": 16.001,
        "endTime": 20.67,
        "duration": 4.67,
        "sentenceIndex": 33
      },
      {
        "text": "She did not know how to continue, so she felt lost and confused.",
        "startTime": 20.67,
        "endTime": 25.723,
        "duration": 5.053,
        "sentenceIndex": 34
      },
      {
        "text": "She did not know if she had enough strength to continue.",
        "startTime": 25.723,
        "endTime": 30.013,
        "duration": 4.29,
        "sentenceIndex": 35
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 30.01288,
    "measuredDuration": 30.01288
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b6",
    "bundleIndex": 6,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-6.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-6.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She whispered, 'Please,' into the quiet room because she wanted help.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5.743,
        "duration": 5.743,
        "sentenceIndex": 36
      },
      {
        "text": "I don’t know how to do this by myself, and I need help.",
        "startTime": 5.743,
        "endTime": 10.231,
        "duration": 4.488,
        "sentenceIndex": 37
      },
      {
        "text": "I do not have the strength to do this right now.",
        "startTime": 10.231,
        "endTime": 14.017,
        "duration": 3.786,
        "sentenceIndex": 38
      },
      {
        "text": "She cried for help until she had no tears left.",
        "startTime": 14.017,
        "endTime": 17.725,
        "duration": 3.707,
        "sentenceIndex": 39
      },
      {
        "text": "Then she went to bed because she expected nothing to change.",
        "startTime": 17.725,
        "endTime": 22.457,
        "duration": 4.733,
        "sentenceIndex": 40
      },
      {
        "text": "The next morning, Lisa's oldest son James came into her room and smiled.",
        "startTime": 22.457,
        "endTime": 28.287,
        "duration": 5.829,
        "sentenceIndex": 41
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 28.286735,
    "measuredDuration": 28.286735
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b7",
    "bundleIndex": 7,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-7.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-7.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "He was six years old and had a toy in his hand.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.237,
        "duration": 3.237,
        "sentenceIndex": 42
      },
      {
        "text": "Mommy,\" he said softly, because he wanted her to listen.",
        "startTime": 3.237,
        "endTime": 7.393,
        "duration": 4.157,
        "sentenceIndex": 43
      },
      {
        "text": "My teacher gave me this gift because I worked hard in class.",
        "startTime": 7.393,
        "endTime": 11.526,
        "duration": 4.132,
        "sentenceIndex": 44
      },
      {
        "text": "James left the room after he put a small package on the table for you.",
        "startTime": 11.526,
        "endTime": 16.346,
        "duration": 4.821,
        "sentenceIndex": 45
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa stayed still for a long time because she was thinking deeply.",
        "startTime": 16.346,
        "endTime": 20.892,
        "duration": 4.545,
        "sentenceIndex": 46
      },
      {
        "text": "She was very tired and felt defeated because she worked hard all day.",
        "startTime": 20.892,
        "endTime": 25.644,
        "duration": 4.752,
        "sentenceIndex": 47
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 25.64356,
    "measuredDuration": 25.64356
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b8",
    "bundleIndex": 8,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-8.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-8.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "But finally, she sat up and looked at the package with curiosity.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.767,
        "duration": 4.767,
        "sentenceIndex": 48
      },
      {
        "text": "The words made her cry again, but this time her tears felt different.",
        "startTime": 4.767,
        "endTime": 9.818,
        "duration": 5.051,
        "sentenceIndex": 49
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa held the package that said \"Parents for Life,\" and she felt something move inside.",
        "startTime": 9.818,
        "endTime": 16.148,
        "duration": 6.33,
        "sentenceIndex": 50
      },
      {
        "text": "She knew at that moment that she must not give up.",
        "startTime": 16.148,
        "endTime": 19.7,
        "duration": 3.552,
        "sentenceIndex": 51
      },
      {
        "text": "Her children needed her because they wanted her help and support every day.",
        "startTime": 19.7,
        "endTime": 25.027,
        "duration": 5.327,
        "sentenceIndex": 52
      },
      {
        "text": "They needed her to be strong and keep going for a better life together.",
        "startTime": 25.027,
        "endTime": 30.07,
        "duration": 5.043,
        "sentenceIndex": 53
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 30.070363,
    "measuredDuration": 30.070363
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b9",
    "bundleIndex": 9,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-9.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-9.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She could not leave them behind because she cared for them deeply.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.689,
        "duration": 4.689,
        "sentenceIndex": 54
      },
      {
        "text": "She did not want to do it, so she wouldn't.",
        "startTime": 4.689,
        "endTime": 7.894,
        "duration": 3.205,
        "sentenceIndex": 55
      },
      {
        "text": "That day, Lisa decided what she wanted to do next.",
        "startTime": 7.894,
        "endTime": 11.597,
        "duration": 3.702,
        "sentenceIndex": 56
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa always dreamed of going back to school and building a career for her children.",
        "startTime": 11.597,
        "endTime": 17.494,
        "duration": 5.897,
        "sentenceIndex": 57
      },
      {
        "text": "She dropped out of high school years ago because life became too complicated.",
        "startTime": 17.494,
        "endTime": 22.965,
        "duration": 5.471,
        "sentenceIndex": 58
      },
      {
        "text": "She told herself it was too late and she had too many responsibilities.",
        "startTime": 22.965,
        "endTime": 28.009,
        "duration": 5.045,
        "sentenceIndex": 59
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 28.009456,
    "measuredDuration": 28.009456
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b10",
    "bundleIndex": 10,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-10.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-10.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Lisa saw the \"Parents for Life\" package on her table and decided to try it.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 5.061,
        "duration": 5.061,
        "sentenceIndex": 60
      },
      {
        "text": "She joined a program to earn her high school diploma because she wants to learn.",
        "startTime": 5.061,
        "endTime": 10.459,
        "duration": 5.398,
        "sentenceIndex": 61
      },
      {
        "text": "She studied at night when the children were asleep and it was quiet.",
        "startTime": 10.459,
        "endTime": 15.047,
        "duration": 4.588,
        "sentenceIndex": 62
      },
      {
        "text": "She studied in the morning because they were still sleeping.",
        "startTime": 15.047,
        "endTime": 19.096,
        "duration": 4.049,
        "sentenceIndex": 63
      },
      {
        "text": "She studied whenever she had free time because she wanted to learn more.",
        "startTime": 19.096,
        "endTime": 23.955,
        "duration": 4.858,
        "sentenceIndex": 64
      },
      {
        "text": "The children became study partners for Lisa, James, Emily, and Noah.",
        "startTime": 23.955,
        "endTime": 28.993,
        "duration": 5.038,
        "sentenceIndex": 65
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 28.992993,
    "measuredDuration": 28.992993
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b11",
    "bundleIndex": 11,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-11.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-11.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "James helped her with flash cards while she cooked dinner.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.902,
        "duration": 3.902,
        "sentenceIndex": 66
      },
      {
        "text": "Emily sat with her when she read her textbooks.",
        "startTime": 3.902,
        "endTime": 7.064,
        "duration": 3.162,
        "sentenceIndex": 67
      },
      {
        "text": "Even little Noah understood that Mommy was doing something very important.",
        "startTime": 7.064,
        "endTime": 12.042,
        "duration": 4.978,
        "sentenceIndex": 68
      },
      {
        "text": "He played quietly while she studied because he knew she needed time.",
        "startTime": 12.042,
        "endTime": 16.617,
        "duration": 4.575,
        "sentenceIndex": 69
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa passed her high school exam, and she felt very happy about it.",
        "startTime": 16.617,
        "endTime": 21.274,
        "duration": 4.657,
        "sentenceIndex": 70
      },
      {
        "text": "Then she signed up for community college because she wanted to learn more.",
        "startTime": 21.274,
        "endTime": 26.252,
        "duration": 4.978,
        "sentenceIndex": 71
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 26.2522,
    "measuredDuration": 26.2522
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b12",
    "bundleIndex": 12,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-12.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-12.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She took online classes to fit her work and her children's needs.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.524,
        "duration": 4.524,
        "sentenceIndex": 72
      },
      {
        "text": "It was not easy, but I tried my best and learned a lot.",
        "startTime": 4.524,
        "endTime": 8.502,
        "duration": 3.978,
        "sentenceIndex": 73
      },
      {
        "text": "There were days when Lisa wanted to quit because she felt like a failure.",
        "startTime": 8.502,
        "endTime": 13.583,
        "duration": 5.081,
        "sentenceIndex": 74
      },
      {
        "text": "But she continued to move forward because she wanted to succeed.",
        "startTime": 13.583,
        "endTime": 18.037,
        "duration": 4.454,
        "sentenceIndex": 75
      },
      {
        "text": "She remembered the package from \"Parents for Life\" because it was very important to her.",
        "startTime": 18.037,
        "endTime": 24.162,
        "duration": 6.125,
        "sentenceIndex": 76
      },
      {
        "text": "She remembered the faces of her children, Lisa, James, Emily, and Noah.",
        "startTime": 24.162,
        "endTime": 29.704,
        "duration": 5.542,
        "sentenceIndex": 77
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 29.703991,
    "measuredDuration": 29.703991
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b13",
    "bundleIndex": 13,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-13.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-13.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "She remembered she must succeed for herself and for her family too.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.479,
        "duration": 4.479,
        "sentenceIndex": 78
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa moved to a university because she wanted to learn more and meet new friends.",
        "startTime": 4.479,
        "endTime": 9.894,
        "duration": 5.415,
        "sentenceIndex": 79
      },
      {
        "text": "She studied social work because she wanted to help families who needed support.",
        "startTime": 9.894,
        "endTime": 15.175,
        "duration": 5.281,
        "sentenceIndex": 80
      },
      {
        "text": "She graduated with honors, so she applied to graduate school after that.",
        "startTime": 15.175,
        "endTime": 20.138,
        "duration": 4.963,
        "sentenceIndex": 81
      },
      {
        "text": "She was accepted into a master's program, so she continued her studies.",
        "startTime": 20.138,
        "endTime": 25.034,
        "duration": 4.896,
        "sentenceIndex": 82
      },
      {
        "text": "Her children, James and Emily, were always with her during everything.",
        "startTime": 25.034,
        "endTime": 30.014,
        "duration": 4.979,
        "sentenceIndex": 83
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 30.01381,
    "measuredDuration": 30.01381
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b14",
    "bundleIndex": 14,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-14.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A2/bundle-14.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "They helped her study for the test because she wanted to do well.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 4.311,
        "duration": 4.311,
        "sentenceIndex": 84
      },
      {
        "text": "They celebrated Lisa's small victories because they were proud of her progress.",
        "startTime": 4.311,
        "endTime": 9.551,
        "duration": 5.24,
        "sentenceIndex": 85
      },
      {
